{"name":"Flip","tagline":"Card flip with js and css","body":"<!--\r\nAuthor Details\r\n==============\r\nAuthor: Ranjith Pandi\r\nAuthor URL: http://ranjithpandi.com\r\nAttribution is must on every page, where this work is used.\r\nFor Attribution removal request. please consider contacting us through http://ranjithpandi.com/#contact\r\n-->\r\n<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title>Flip card on click and mouse over</title>\r\n<style>\r\n.flipdiv, .flipdiv1 {\r\nwidth: 300px;\r\nheight: 300px;\r\nposition: relative;\r\nfloat: left;\r\nmargin-right: 10px;\r\n-webkit-transition: -webkit-transform 1s;\r\n-moz-transition: -moz-transform 1s;\r\n-o-transition: -o-transform 1s;\r\ntransition: transform 1s;\r\n-webkit-transform-style: preserve-3d;\r\n-moz-transform-style: preserve-3d;\r\n-o-transform-style: preserve-3d;\r\ntransform-style: preserve-3d;\r\n}\r\n.flipdiv:hover, .turned {\r\n-webkit-transform: rotateY( 180deg );\r\n-moz-transform: rotateY( 180deg );\r\n-o-transform: rotateY( 180deg );\r\ntransform: rotateY( 180deg );\r\n}\r\n.flipdiv div, .flipdiv1 div {\r\nwidth: 300px;\r\nheight: 300px;\r\nline-height: 150px;\r\ncolor: white;\r\ntext-align: center;\r\nfont-weight: bold;\r\nfont-size: 50px;\r\nposition: absolute;\r\nborder-radius: 15px;\r\ncursor: pointer;\r\n-webkit-backface-visibility: hidden;\r\n-moz-backface-visibility: hidden;\r\n-o-backface-visibility: hidden;\r\nbackface-visibility: hidden;\r\n}\r\n.front {\r\nbackground: red;\r\n}\r\n.back {\r\nbackground: blue;\r\n-webkit-transform: rotateY( 180deg );\r\n-moz-transform: rotateY( 180deg );\r\n-o-transform: rotateY( 180deg );\r\ntransform: rotateY( 180deg );\r\n}\r\n</style>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"flipdiv\">\r\n<div class=\"front\">Front</div>\r\n<div class=\"back\">Back</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"flipdiv1\">\r\n<div class=\"front\">Front</div>\r\n<div class=\"back\">Back</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"http://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.11.1/jquery.min.js\"></script>\r\n<script>\r\n$(\".flipdiv1\").on('click', function(){\r\n$(this).toggleClass('turned');\r\n});\r\n</script>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>","google":"","note":"Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration."}